@startuml
[*] --> DisplayJourneyDetails : user logs in and selects destination
DisplayJourneyDetails --> ActivateDrivingMode : activate driving mode selected
DisplayJourneyDetails --> ChooseOtherOptions : choose other options selected
DisplayJourneyDetails --> SelectPlaceToEat : select place to eat
SelectPlaceToEat --> ViewMenu : view menu
ViewMenu --> PlaceOrder : order food
DisplayJourneyDetails --> InformAuthorities : accident occurs
DisplayJourneyDetails --> SendNotifications : driving or accident event detected
JourneyCompleted --> ProvideFeedback : provide feedback after journey completion
@enduml
